data.description: REDUCED for quick sell!!!!!! Home freshly painted features 5 Bedrooms (2 down & 3 up), 3 Bath (2 down/1up), 2 car Garage in quiet cove. Formal living & Dining rm, large Den, Eat in Kit., Laundry rm and large Game rm upstairs. Refinished original Hardwood thru out except Den(laminate) and ceramic tile in kitchen and bath(s). Roof is less than 1 year old, new hot water heater & dishwasher. Large fenced backyard w/storage building. Plenty of space. Bring all offers!! Schedule your private showing.
